Your questions, answered

What is Airbnb and how does it work?
We verify personal profiles and listings to make sharing easy, enjoyable, and safe for millions of Hosts and travelers worldwide. Find out more about Airbnb.
How do I use search filters?
Its easy to use our search filters to only show the listings that have the features you need. Learn more about using search filters and discover more flexible ways to search.
Do I need to meet my Host?
Options like self check-in or booking an entire home allow you to interact with your Host mainly through in-app messagingyou can message them anytime if something comes up.
What if I need to cancel due to a problem with the listing or Host?
In most cases, you can resolve any issues directly by messaging your host. If they can't help, simply contact Airbnb within 24 hours of discovering the issue. Learn more
Need more information?
Visit our Help Center to get additional answers to your questions. Learn more
